---
title: One-Pan Mushroom Ravioli Gratin with a Crispy Parmesan Crust
description: *Gratin* is a fancy French way of saying this dish is topped with cheesy breadcrumbs and heated under the broiler until brown and crispy. So it essentially translates to “delicious,” right? But just in case you need another reason to give this recipe a shot, let us point out that you can make it in only one pot. Talk about an easy cleanup.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5cc204560c391500160e8325-e51a0406.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/one-pan-mushroom-ravioli-gratin-5cc204560c391500160e8325-7ca09919.pdf
course: main course
